This repository is a modified and extended distribution based on the
TradingAgents open-source project from TauricResearch:
https://github.com/TauricResearch/TradingAgents

This repository is not an official release of TauricResearch.

Major modifications in this distribution include:
- Chinese dashboard and local one-click startup flow for Windows
- A-share oriented single-stock analysis workflow
- Overnight scanner, review, validation, and dashboard integration
- Structured factor snapshots and rule-constrained decision summaries
- Optional QVeris supplement routes for A-share overnight scanning
- Additional deployment scripts, tests, and compatibility fixes

